         <div type="diary-day" xml:id="entry__1923-07-16">
            <p xml:space="preserve"><date when="1923-07-16">16/7</date> Vm. dictirt (Rekurs Erwerb Steuer u. a.) (<rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_1912">Med. Film</rs>).</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Nm. <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_69902" ref="#person_13356"><roleName>Dr.</roleName> <surname>Bachrach</surname></rs> (Sascha), <rs type="work" subtype="self" xml:id="bibl_1913">Med. Film</rs> Aenderungen.―</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">Bei <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_69903" ref="#person_13551"><forename>Richard</forename></rs>; <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_69904" ref="#person_20200"><roleName>Dr.</roleName> <surname>Sonne</surname></rs>; <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_69905" ref="#person_13550"><forename>Paula</forename></rs> und die Mädeln. Verlegergeschichten, 
<rs type="place" xml:id="pl_14862" ref="#place_e884124295d0c4d07d9bcf5096fd5495">Amerika</rs>, <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_69906" ref="#person_15009"><surname>Fischer</surname></rs> etc.―</p>
            <p xml:space="preserve" rend="indent">N. d. N. bei <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_69907" ref="#person_19784"><surname>Schmutzers</surname></rs>, wo <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_69908" ref="#person_13551"><forename>Richard</forename></rs> und <rs type="person" xml:id="pNt_69909" ref="#person_13550"><forename>Paula</forename></rs>. Im Atelier, dann im Garten.</p>
         </div>
